        <mxCell id="termtext" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Courier New;fontSize=12;fontColor=#D4D4D4;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;font color=&quot;#4EC9B0&quot;&gt;root@nginx-01:~#&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#DCDCAA&quot;&gt;systemctl status nginx-wd-a&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#9CDCFE&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;nginx-wd-a.service&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#CE9178&quot;&gt;&quot;System Resource Monitor A&quot;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#F48771&quot;&gt;← 실제: watchdog A&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#6A7A6A&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Active: active (running)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#4EC9B0&quot;&gt;root@nginx-01:~#&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#DCDCAA&quot;&gt;ps aux | grep kworker&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#D4D4D4&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;root 2103 [kworker/2:1]&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#F48771&quot;&gt;← 실제: .kworker-mon (커널스레드와 유사 명명)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#4EC9B0&quot;&gt;root@nginx-01:~#&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#DCDCAA&quot;&gt;ls /usr/local/bin | grep guard&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#808080&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(출력 없음)&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#F48771&quot;&gt;← .unmask-guard · .fw-guard = 점 파일, ls 에 안 보임&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#4EC9B0&quot;&gt;root@nginx-01:~#&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#DCDCAA&quot;&gt;systemctl stop nginx-wd-a ; systemctl mask nginx&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#6A9955&quot;&gt;# 5초 후 → watchdog B가 A 부활 · unmask-guard가 nginx unmask&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#6A9955&quot;&gt;# 단순 grep/ls 는 지연되지만 systemctl list-units · ls -la 엔 그대로 보임&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#4EC9B0&quot;&gt;root@nginx-01:~#&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#DCDCAA&quot;&gt;crontab -l | grep wd&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#D4D4D4&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;* * * * * pgrep nginx-wd-a || nohup nginx-wd-a&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#F48771&quot;&gt;← 1분 백업 부활&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#4EC9B0&quot;&gt;root@nginx-01:~#&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#AEAFAD&quot;&gt;▋&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="430" width="560" x="914" y="146" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="lg" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=10;fontColor=#5F5E5A;" value="범례 — 보라 watchdog · 청록 무결성 보장 · 초록 cron · 시안 독립 데몬(systemd 밖) · 양방향 화살표 = 상호 부활 · 점선 카드 = systemd 밖에서 동작" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="18" width="1300" x="40" y="596" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
